<section id="standardJournalItem">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>standard journals</primary>
      <secondary>adding transactions to</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>general ledger</primary>
      <secondary>entering in standard journal</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>transactions</primary>
      <secondary>adding to standard journal</secondary>
    </indexterm>Standard Journal Item</title>
  <para>To add a new transaction to a Journal, select the NEW button. The
  following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/standardJournalItem.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Add New Journal Transaction</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When adding a new transaction to a Journal, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Amount</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify the monetary value of the transaction.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Sense</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Choose one of the following options:</para>
        <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>Debit</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>Select if transaction Debits specified Account.</para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>Credit</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>Select if transaction Credits specified Account.</para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Account</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify the Account to be used for the transaction
        record.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
